  "root_text": {
    "snp1.3:0.1": "Sutta Nipāta 1.3 ",
    "snp1.3:0.2": "Khaggavisāṇasutta ",
    "snp1.3:1.1": "“Sabbesu bhūtesu nidhāya daṇḍaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:1.2": "Aviheṭhayaṁ aññatarampi tesaṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:1.3": "Na puttamiccheyya kuto sahāyaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:1.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:2.1": "“Saṁsaggajātassa bhavanti snehā, ",
    "snp1.3:2.2": "Snehanvayaṁ dukkhamidaṁ pahoti; ",
    "snp1.3:2.3": "Ādīnavaṁ snehajaṁ pekkhamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:2.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:3.1": "“Mitte suhajje anukampamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:3.2": "Hāpeti atthaṁ paṭibaddhacitto; ",
    "snp1.3:3.3": "Etaṁ bhayaṁ santhave pekkhamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:3.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:4.1": "“Vaṁso visālova yathā visatto, ",
    "snp1.3:4.2": "Puttesu dāresu ca yā apekkhā; ",
    "snp1.3:4.3": "Vaṁsakkaḷīrova asajjamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:4.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:5.1": "“Migo araññamhi yathā abaddho, ",
    "snp1.3:5.2": "Yenicchakaṁ gacchati gocarāya; ",
    "snp1.3:5.3": "Viññū naro seritaṁ pekkhamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:5.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:6.1": "“Āmantanā hoti sahāyamajjhe, ",
    "snp1.3:6.2": "Vāse ṭhāne gamane cārikāya; ",
    "snp1.3:6.3": "Anabhijjhitaṁ seritaṁ pekkhamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:6.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:7.1": "“Khiḍḍā ratī hoti sahāyamajjhe, ",
    "snp1.3:7.2": "Puttesu ca vipulaṁ hoti pemaṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:7.3": "Piyavippayogaṁ vijigucchamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:7.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:8.1": "“Cātuddiso appaṭigho ca hoti, ",
    "snp1.3:8.2": "Santussamāno itarītarena; ",
    "snp1.3:8.3": "Parissayānaṁ sahitā achambhī, ",
    "snp1.3:8.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:9.1": "“Dussaṅgahā pabbajitāpi eke, ",
    "snp1.3:9.2": "Atho gahaṭṭhā gharamāvasantā; ",
    "snp1.3:9.3": "Appossukko paraputtesu hutvā, ",
    "snp1.3:9.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:10.1": "“Oropayitvā gihibyañjanāni, ",
    "snp1.3:10.2": "Sañchinnapatto yathā koviḷāro; ",
    "snp1.3:10.3": "Chetvāna vīro gihibandhanāni, ",
    "snp1.3:10.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:11.1": "“Sace labhetha nipakaṁ sahāyaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:11.2": "Saddhiṁ caraṁ sādhuvihāridhīraṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:11.3": "Abhibhuyya sabbāni parissayāni, ",
    "snp1.3:11.4": "Careyya tenattamano satīmā”. ",
    "snp1.3:12.1": "“No ce labhetha nipakaṁ sahāyaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:12.2": "Saddhiṁ caraṁ sādhuvihāridhīraṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:12.3": "Rājāva raṭṭhaṁ vijitaṁ pahāya, ",
    "snp1.3:12.4": "Eko care mātaṅgaraññeva nāgo”. ",
    "snp1.3:13.1": "“Addhā pasaṁsāma sahāyasampadaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:13.2": "Seṭṭhā samā sevitabbā sahāyā; ",
    "snp1.3:13.3": "Ete aladdhā anavajjabhojī, ",
    "snp1.3:13.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:14.1": "“Disvā suvaṇṇassa pabhassarāni, ",
    "snp1.3:14.2": "Kammāraputtena suniṭṭhitāni; ",
    "snp1.3:14.3": "Saṅghaṭṭamānāni duve bhujasmiṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:14.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:15.1": "“Evaṁ dutīyena sahā mamassa, ",
    "snp1.3:15.2": "Vācābhilāpo abhisajjanā vā; ",
    "snp1.3:15.3": "Etaṁ bhayaṁ āyatiṁ pekkhamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:15.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:16.1": "“Kāmā hi citrā madhurā manoramā, ",
    "snp1.3:16.2": "Virūparūpena mathenti cittaṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:16.3": "Ādīnavaṁ kāmaguṇesu disvā, ",
    "snp1.3:16.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:17.1": "“Ītī ca gaṇḍo ca upaddavo ca, ",
    "snp1.3:17.2": "Rogo ca sallañca bhayañca metaṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:17.3": "Etaṁ bhayaṁ kāmaguṇesu disvā, ",
    "snp1.3:17.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:18.1": "“Sītañca uṇhañca khudaṁ pipāsaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:18.2": "Vātātape ḍaṁsasarīsape ca; ",
    "snp1.3:18.3": "Sabbānipetāni abhisambhavitvā, ",
    "snp1.3:18.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:19.1": "“Nāgova yūthāni vivajjayitvā, ",
    "snp1.3:19.2": "Sañjātakhandho padumī uḷāro; ",
    "snp1.3:19.3": "Yathābhirantaṁ viharaṁ araññe, ",
    "snp1.3:19.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:20.1": "“Aṭṭhānataṁ saṅgaṇikāratassa, ",
    "snp1.3:20.2": "Yaṁ phassaye sāmayikaṁ vimuttiṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:20.3": "Ādiccabandhussa vaco nisamma, ",
    "snp1.3:20.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:21.1": "“Diṭṭhīvisūkāni upātivatto, ",
    "snp1.3:21.2": "Patto niyāmaṁ paṭiladdhamaggo; ",
    "snp1.3:21.3": "Uppannañāṇomhi anaññaneyyo, ",
    "snp1.3:21.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:22.1": "“Nillolupo nikkuho nippipāso, ",
    "snp1.3:22.2": "Nimmakkho niddhantakasāvamoho; ",
    "snp1.3:22.3": "Nirāsayo sabbaloke bhavitvā, ",
    "snp1.3:22.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:23.1": "“Pāpaṁ sahāyaṁ parivajjayetha, ",
    "snp1.3:23.2": "Anatthadassiṁ visame niviṭṭhaṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:23.3": "Sayaṁ na seve pasutaṁ pamattaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:23.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:24.1": "“Bahussutaṁ dhammadharaṁ bhajetha, ",
    "snp1.3:24.2": "Mittaṁ uḷāraṁ paṭibhānavantaṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:24.3": "Aññāya atthāni vineyya kaṅkhaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:24.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:25.1": "“Khiḍḍaṁ ratiṁ kāmasukhañca loke, ",
    "snp1.3:25.2": "Analaṅkaritvā anapekkhamāno; ",
    "snp1.3:25.3": "Vibhūsanaṭṭhānā virato saccavādī, ",
    "snp1.3:25.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:26.1": "“Puttañca dāraṁ pitarañca mātaraṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:26.2": "Dhanāni dhaññāni ca bandhavāni; ",
    "snp1.3:26.3": "Hitvāna kāmāni yathodhikāni, ",
    "snp1.3:26.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:27.1": "“Saṅgo eso parittamettha sokhyaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:27.2": "Appassādo dukkhamettha bhiyyo; ",
    "snp1.3:27.3": "Gaḷo eso iti ñatvā matīmā, ",
    "snp1.3:27.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:28.1": "“Sandālayitvāna saṁyojanāni, ",
    "snp1.3:28.2": "Jālaṁva bhetvā salilambucārī; ",
    "snp1.3:28.3": "Aggīva daḍḍhaṁ anivattamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:28.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:29.1": "“Okkhittacakkhu na ca pādalolo, ",
    "snp1.3:29.2": "Guttindriyo rakkhitamānasāno; ",
    "snp1.3:29.3": "Anavassuto apariḍayhamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:29.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:30.1": "“Ohārayitvā gihibyañjanāni, ",
    "snp1.3:30.2": "Sañchannapatto yathā pārichatto; ",
    "snp1.3:30.3": "Kāsāyavattho abhinikkhamitvā, ",
    "snp1.3:30.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:31.1": "“Rasesu gedhaṁ akaraṁ alolo, ",
    "snp1.3:31.2": "Anaññaposī sapadānacārī; ",
    "snp1.3:31.3": "Kule kule appaṭibaddhacitto, ",
    "snp1.3:31.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:32.1": "“Pahāya pañcāvaraṇāni cetaso, ",
    "snp1.3:32.2": "Upakkilese byapanujja sabbe; ",
    "snp1.3:32.3": "Anissito chetva sinehadosaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:32.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:33.1": "“Vipiṭṭhikatvāna sukhaṁ dukhañca, ",
    "snp1.3:33.2": "Pubbeva ca somanassadomanassaṁ; ",
    "snp1.3:33.3": "Laddhānupekkhaṁ samathaṁ visuddhaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:33.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:34.1": "“Āraddhaviriyo paramatthapattiyā, ",
    "snp1.3:34.2": "Alīnacitto akusītavutti; ",
    "snp1.3:34.3": "Daḷhanikkamo thāmabalūpapanno, ",
    "snp1.3:34.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:35.1": "“Paṭisallānaṁ jhānamariñcamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:35.2": "Dhammesu niccaṁ anudhammacārī; ",
    "snp1.3:35.3": "Ādīnavaṁ sammasitā bhavesu, ",
    "snp1.3:35.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:36.1": "“Taṇhakkhayaṁ patthayamappamatto, ",
    "snp1.3:36.2": "Aneḷamūgo sutavā satīmā; ",
    "snp1.3:36.3": "Saṅkhātadhammo niyato padhānavā, ",
    "snp1.3:36.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:37.1": "“Sīhova saddesu asantasanto, ",
    "snp1.3:37.2": "Vātova jālamhi asajjamāno; ",
    "snp1.3:37.3": "Padumaṁva toyena alippamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:37.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:38.1": "“Sīho yathā dāṭhabalī pasayha, ",
    "snp1.3:38.2": "Rājā migānaṁ abhibhuyya cārī; ",
    "snp1.3:38.3": "Sevetha pantāni senāsanāni, ",
    "snp1.3:38.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:39.1": "“Mettaṁ upekkhaṁ karuṇaṁ vimuttiṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:39.2": "Āsevamāno muditañca kāle; ",
    "snp1.3:39.3": "Sabbena lokena avirujjhamāno, ",
    "snp1.3:39.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:40.1": "“Rāgañca dosañca pahāya mohaṁ, ",
    "snp1.3:40.2": "Sandālayitvāna saṁyojanāni; ",
    "snp1.3:40.3": "Asantasaṁ jīvitasaṅkhayamhi, ",
    "snp1.3:40.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:41.1": "“Bhajanti sevanti ca kāraṇatthā, ",
    "snp1.3:41.2": "Nikkāraṇā dullabhā ajja mittā; ",
    "snp1.3:41.3": "Attaṭṭhapaññā asucī manussā, ",
    "snp1.3:41.4": "Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo”. ",
    "snp1.3:41.5": "Khaggavisāṇasuttaṁ tatiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "snp1.3:0.1": "Anthology of Discourses 1.3 ",
    "snp1.3:0.2": "The Horned Rhino ",
    "snp1.3:1.1": "When you’ve laid down arms toward all creatures, ",
    "snp1.3:1.2": "not harming even a single one, ",
    "snp1.3:1.3": "don’t wish for a child, let alone a companion: ",
    "snp1.3:1.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:2.1": "Those with close relationships have affection, ",
    "snp1.3:2.2": "following which this pain arises. ",
    "snp1.3:2.3": "Seeing this danger born of affection, ",
    "snp1.3:2.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:3.1": "When feelings for friends and loved ones ",
    "snp1.3:3.2": "are tied up in selfish love, you miss out on the goal. ",
    "snp1.3:3.3": "Seeing this peril in intimacy, ",
    "snp1.3:3.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:4.1": "As a spreading bamboo gets entangled, ",
    "snp1.3:4.2": "so does concern for partners and children. ",
    "snp1.3:4.3": "Like a bamboo shoot unobstructed, ",
    "snp1.3:4.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:5.1": "As a wild deer loose in the forest ",
    "snp1.3:5.2": "grazes wherever it wants, ",
    "snp1.3:5.3": "a smart person looking for freedom would ",
    "snp1.3:5.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:6.1": "When among friends, whether staying in place ",
    "snp1.3:6.2": "or going on a journey, you’re always on call. ",
    "snp1.3:6.3": "Looking for the uncoveted freedom, ",
    "snp1.3:6.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:7.1": "Among friends you have fun and games, ",
    "snp1.3:7.2": "and for children you are full of fondness. ",
    "snp1.3:7.3": "Though loathe to depart from those you hold dear, ",
    "snp1.3:7.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:8.1": "At ease in any quarter, unresisting, ",
    "snp1.3:8.2": "content with whatever comes your way; ",
    "snp1.3:8.3": "prevailing over adversities, dauntless, ",
    "snp1.3:8.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:9.1": "Even some renunciates are hard to please, ",
    "snp1.3:9.2": "as are some layfolk dwelling at home. ",
    "snp1.3:9.3": "Don’t worry about others’ children, ",
    "snp1.3:9.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:10.1": "Having shed the marks of the home life, ",
    "snp1.3:10.2": "like the fallen leaves of the Shady Orchid Tree; ",
    "snp1.3:10.3": "having cut the bonds of the home life, a hero would ",
    "snp1.3:10.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:11.1": "If you find an alert companion, ",
    "snp1.3:11.2": "an attentive friend to live happily together, ",
    "snp1.3:11.3": "then, overcoming all adversities, ",
    "snp1.3:11.4": "wander with them, joyful and mindful. ",
    "snp1.3:12.1": "If you find no alert companion, ",
    "snp1.3:12.2": "an attentive friend to live happily together, ",
    "snp1.3:12.3": "then, like a king who flees his conquered realm, ",
    "snp1.3:12.4": "wander alone like a tusker in the wilds. ",
    "snp1.3:13.1": "Clearly we praise the blessing of a friend, ",
    "snp1.3:13.2": "it’s good to be with friends your equal or better. ",
    "snp1.3:13.3": "but failing to find them, eating blamelessly, ",
    "snp1.3:13.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:14.1": "Though made of shining gold, <j>well-finished by a smith, ",
    "snp1.3:14.2": "when two bracelets share the same arm ",
    "snp1.3:14.3": "they clash up against each other. Seeing this, ",
    "snp1.3:14.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:15.1": "Thinking, “So too, if I had a partner, ",
    "snp1.3:15.2": "there’d be flattery or curses.” ",
    "snp1.3:15.3": "Seeing this peril in the future, ",
    "snp1.3:15.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:16.1": "Sensual pleasures are diverse, sweet, delightful, ",
    "snp1.3:16.2": "appearing in disguise they disturb the mind. ",
    "snp1.3:16.3": "Seeing danger in sensual stimulations, ",
    "snp1.3:16.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:17.1": "This is a calamity, a boil, a disaster, ",
    "snp1.3:17.2": "an illness, a dart, and a danger for me. ",
    "snp1.3:17.3": "Seeing this peril in sensuality, ",
    "snp1.3:17.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:18.1": "Heat and cold, hunger and thirst, ",
    "snp1.3:18.2": "wind and sun, flies and snakes: ",
    "snp1.3:18.3": "having put up with all these things, ",
    "snp1.3:18.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:19.1": "As a full-grown elephant, lotus-fond, magnificent, ",
    "snp1.3:19.2": "forsaking the herd, ",
    "snp1.3:19.3": "stays as it pleases in the forest, ",
    "snp1.3:19.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:20.1": "It’s impossible for one who delights in company ",
    "snp1.3:20.2": "to experience even temporary freedom. ",
    "snp1.3:20.3": "Heeding the speech of the Kinsman of the Sun, ",
    "snp1.3:20.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:21.1": "Thinking, “I have left twisted views behind, ",
    "snp1.3:21.2": "reached the sure way, and gained the path; ",
    "snp1.3:21.3": "I’ve given rise to knowledge, <j>and need no-one to guide me”, ",
    "snp1.3:21.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:22.1": "No greed, no guile, no thirst, no slur, ",
    "snp1.3:22.2": "dross and delusion is smelted off; ",
    "snp1.3:22.3": "free of hoping for anything in the world, ",
    "snp1.3:22.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:23.1": "Avoid a wicked companion, ",
    "snp1.3:23.2": "blind to the good, habitually immoral. ",
    "snp1.3:23.3": "Don’t befriend the heedless and the hankering, but ",
    "snp1.3:23.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:24.1": "Spend time with the learned <j>who have memorized the teachings, ",
    "snp1.3:24.2": "an eloquent and uplifting friend. ",
    "snp1.3:24.3": "When you understand the meanings <j>and have dispelled doubt, ",
    "snp1.3:24.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:25.1": "When you realize that worldly fun and games ",
    "snp1.3:25.2": "and pleasure are inadequate, <j>unconcerned with them, ",
    "snp1.3:25.3": "as one unadorned, a speaker of truth, ",
    "snp1.3:25.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:26.1": "Children, partner, father, mother, ",
    "snp1.3:26.2": "wealth and grain and relatives: ",
    "snp1.3:26.3": "having given up sensual pleasures to this extent, ",
    "snp1.3:26.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:27.1": "“This is a chain. Here there’s hardly any happiness, ",
    "snp1.3:27.2": "little gratification, and it’s full of drawbacks. ",
    "snp1.3:27.3": "It’s a hook.” Knowing this, a thoughtful person would ",
    "snp1.3:27.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:28.1": "Having burst apart the fetters, ",
    "snp1.3:28.2": "like a fish that tears the net and swims free, ",
    "snp1.3:28.3": "or a fire not returning to ground it has burned, ",
    "snp1.3:28.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:29.1": "Eyes downcast, not footloose, ",
    "snp1.3:29.2": "senses guarded, mind protected, ",
    "snp1.3:29.3": "not festering or burning with desire, ",
    "snp1.3:29.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:30.1": "Having shed the marks of the home life, ",
    "snp1.3:30.2": "like the fallen leaves of the Shady Orchid Tree, ",
    "snp1.3:30.3": "and gone forth in the ocher robe, ",
    "snp1.3:30.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:31.1": "Not wanton, nor rousing greed for tastes, ",
    "snp1.3:31.2": "providing for no other, <j>wandering indiscriminately for alms, ",
    "snp1.3:31.3": "not attached to this family or that, ",
    "snp1.3:31.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:32.1": "When you’ve given up five mental obstacles, ",
    "snp1.3:32.2": "and cast aside all corruptions, ",
    "snp1.3:32.3": "and cut off affection and hate, being independent, ",
    "snp1.3:32.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:33.1": "When you’ve put pleasure and pain behind you, ",
    "snp1.3:33.2": "and former happiness and sadness, ",
    "snp1.3:33.3": "and gained equanimity serene and pure, ",
    "snp1.3:33.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:34.1": "With energy roused to reach the ultimate goal, ",
    "snp1.3:34.2": "not sluggish in mind or lazy, ",
    "snp1.3:34.3": "vigorous, strong and powerful, ",
    "snp1.3:34.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:35.1": "Not neglecting retreat and absorption, ",
    "snp1.3:35.2": "always living in line with the teaching, ",
    "snp1.3:35.3": "comprehending the danger in rebirths, ",
    "snp1.3:35.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:36.1": "One whose aim is the ending of craving—",
    "snp1.3:36.2": "diligent, clever, learned, mindful, resolute—",
    "snp1.3:36.3": "who has appraised the teaching and is destined for awakening, should ",
    "snp1.3:36.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:37.1": "Like a lion not startled by sounds, ",
    "snp1.3:37.2": "like wind not caught in a net, ",
    "snp1.3:37.3": "like water not sticking to a lotus, ",
    "snp1.3:37.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:38.1": "Like the fierce-fanged lion, king of beasts, ",
    "snp1.3:38.2": "who wanders as conqueror and victor, ",
    "snp1.3:38.3": "you should frequent remote lodgings, and ",
    "snp1.3:38.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:39.1": "In time, cultivate freedom through ",
    "snp1.3:39.2": "love, compassion, rejoicing, and equanimity. ",
    "snp1.3:39.3": "Not upset by anything in the world, ",
    "snp1.3:39.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:40.1": "Having given up greed, hate, and delusion, ",
    "snp1.3:40.2": "having burst apart the fetters, ",
    "snp1.3:40.3": "unafraid at the end of life, ",
    "snp1.3:40.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. ",
    "snp1.3:41.1": "They befriend you and serve you for their own sake; ",
    "snp1.3:41.2": "these days it’s hard to find friends <j>lacking ulterior motive. ",
    "snp1.3:41.3": "Impure folk cleverly profit themselves—",
    "snp1.3:41.4": "live alone like a horned rhino. "
  },
